{"tid":285871,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"東方鈦業發生大火 鈦白粉市場繼續升溫","createTime":"2017-06-16T07:20:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-18T07:59:50.000Z","uid":51183,"like":159,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"976a9a94ba460a6d10c28d492079f9306fb66fae","tid":285871,"uid":51183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T07:20:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://read01.com/3MmExy.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fread01.com%2F3MmExy.html&d=gdRW82Wprm0QCynl%2BG%2BEj3Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=4ac10038\" target=\"_blank\">https://read01.com/3MmExy.html</a><br />\n<br />\n金投現貨網（<a href=\"https://xianhuo.cngold.org/）03月23日訊，2017年3月23日，化工廠事故每年都有，每一次事故都勞民傷財，造成的人員傷亡也讓人很心痛。各大廠家注意廠區安全，防範結合，預防為主。\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fxianhuo.cngold.org%2F%EF%BC%8903%E6%9C%8823%E6%97%A5%E8%A8%8A%EF%BC%8C2017%E5%B9%B43%E6%9C%8823%E6%97%A5%EF%BC%8C%E5%8C%96%E5%B7%A5%E5%BB%A0%E4%BA%8B%E6%95%85%E6%AF%8F%E5%B9%B4%E9%83%BD%E6%9C%89%EF%BC%8C%E6%AF%8F%E4%B8%80%E6%AC%A1%E4%BA%8B%E6%95%85%E9%83%BD%E5%8B%9E%E6%B0%91%E5%82%B7%E8%B2%A1%EF%BC%8C%E9%80%A0%E6%88%90%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E5%82%B7%E4%BA%A1%E4%B9%9F%E8%AE%93%E4%BA%BA%E5%BE%88%E5%BF%83%E7%97%9B%E3%80%82%E5%90%84%E5%A4%A7%E5%BB%A0%E5%AE%B6%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%E5%BB%A0%E5%8D%80%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%EF%BC%8C%E9%98%B2%E7%AF%84%E7%B5%90%E5%90%88%EF%BC%8C%E9%A0%90%E9%98%B2%E7%82%BA%E4%B8%BB%E3%80%82&d=gdRW82Wprm0QCynl%2BG%2BEj3Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=e877330c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://xianhuo.cngold.org/）03月23日訊，2017年3月23日，化工廠事故每年都有，每一次事故都勞民傷財，造成的人員傷亡也讓人很心痛。各大廠家注意廠區安全，防範結合，預防為主。</a><br />\n<br />\n就在昨天下午1點左右，四川攀枝花米易縣埡口鎮一枝山工業園區內，東方鈦業礦石泥漿過濾崗位樓發生火災。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，攀枝花119指揮中心接到報警電話後，立即出動6個消防中隊14輛消防車、65名消防官兵到達現場進行火災撲救。截止16時20分，火災被完全撲滅。火災無人員受傷，無爆炸、毒害等危害。目前，起火原因正在調查中。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然此次事故並未造成人員傷亡，但是還是給廣大的企業廠商敲起了警鐘。生產很重要，但是安全更重要。<br />\n<br />\n近期，國內鈦白粉市場需求旺盛，本一路上漲至高位的鈦白粉價格，受到此次事故的影響預計還會繼續升溫。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有無人知3個月前東方大火<br />\n鈦白粉降番價未?"},{"pid":"8ecb398f91ae67f646a54082d8592411f9c771f3","tid":285871,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T07:26:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d323084f96147345e1ddc9339802d6a4fa231adb","tid":285871,"uid":26506,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T07:30:36.000Z","msg":"有冇人知鈦白粉同太白粉商品市場喺亞洲嘅交易時段喺咩時候? 消息可從何得知?"},{"pid":"2faf934c9482372c60a5edd2eb2e3bdff2fa5e18","tid":285871,"uid":59753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T07:40:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"413c81ce0e8fb203a6da26ed20809c146e1d82f2","tid":285871,"uid":74262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T07:40:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d9ca6ed504e20f72f5648ea221fec7d23d7052d1","tid":285871,"uid":42767,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T07:42:48.000Z","msg":"鈦太粉含金量高"},{"pid":"f69c1d8df63b347f40e9cf36e1e394a8465c644f","tid":285871,"uid":42767,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T07:43:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鈦白粉含金量高</blockquote>"},{"pid":"07024771c2d44ea457917bd4d8a8d0a68de0f343","tid":285871,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T07:59:14.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"b8294a42d52d97704de936a3efbba006a721af6a","tid":285871,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T08:00:44.000Z","msg":"台灣有冇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7833323da900dfd5f9f64d9bbf717324ddc6318","tid":285871,"uid":44318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T08:01:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/as